  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/c0fffd604b82b29492d9d66ef7a01c94.avif?t=1744958238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras_big/c0fffd604b82b29492d9d66ef7a01c94.avif?t=1744958238 width=800 height=358 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Skyeisle Cube\" is a 3D block elimination game.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each number represents a battle of wits.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every tap releases creativity.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sculpting of each piece is an artistic cleansing of the soul.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mysterious shapes hidden behind colorful blocks and explore the infinite possibilities of sculptural art!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Explore Structures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Discover fascinating formations made of solid blue blocks and irregular pink blocks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Number Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Pay attention to the numbers on the outer surfaces—they reveal the block arrangements in horizontal, vertical, and depth directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/df17081cfa37759408ba074c2f624087.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/df17081cfa37759408ba074c2f624087.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/df17081cfa37759408ba074c2f624087.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Success Awaits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  As the hidden structure within the cube gradually reveals itself, you'll know success is near. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/6be29476e15e37029d89e8c99a3b101c.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/6be29476e15e37029d89e8c99a3b101c.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/6be29476e15e37029d89e8c99a3b101c.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Gentle Tribute</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  In \"Skyeisle Cube,\" every detail is a gentle tribute to the beauty of life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/e79a43cf467535d3cc2278875bb93a59.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/e79a43cf467535d3cc2278875bb93a59.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/e79a43cf467535d3cc2278875bb93a59.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Dreamlike Light and Shadow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our artists have carefully crafted each color, making light and shadow dance on the cubes to create a world that is both realistic and dreamlike. From intricate textures to smooth animations, every block seems to breathe, and each click reveals their vitality. Experience serene streams and idyllic pastures, snowy celebrations, and the wild beauty of distant shores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f8002c7e0f89448ec384a15fabb0d3ae.avif?t=1744958238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras_big/f8002c7e0f89448ec384a15fabb0d3ae.avif?t=1744958238 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Life's Tapestry</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tiny sky island is a beautiful depiction of the life we dream of, capturing the moments we wish to experience beyond our daily routines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At present, the DEMO test session has been opened</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have any suggestions during the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to contact us~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E-mail: <a href=\"mailto:3941637341@qq.com\">3941637341@qq.com</a></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/c0fffd604b82b29492d9d66ef7a01c94.avif?t=1744958238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras_big/c0fffd604b82b29492d9d66ef7a01c94.avif?t=1744958238 width=800 height=358 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Skyeisle Cube\" is a 3D block elimination game.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each number represents a battle of wits.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every tap releases creativity.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sculpting of each piece is an artistic cleansing of the soul.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mysterious shapes hidden behind colorful blocks and explore the infinite possibilities of sculptural art!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Explore Structures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Discover fascinating formations made of solid blue blocks and irregular pink blocks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Number Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Pay attention to the numbers on the outer surfaces—they reveal the block arrangements in horizontal, vertical, and depth directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted l