 src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/e79a43cf467535d3cc2278875bb93a59.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Dreamlike Light and Shadow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our artists have carefully crafted each color, making light and shadow dance on the cubes to create a world that is both realistic and dreamlike. From intricate textures to smooth animations, every block seems to breathe, and each click reveals their vitality. Experience serene streams and idyllic pastures, snowy celebrations, and the wild beauty of distant shores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f8002c7e0f89448ec384a15fabb0d3ae.avif?t=1744958238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras_big/f8002c7e0f89448ec384a15fabb0d3ae.avif?t=1744958238 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-Life's Tapestry</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tiny sky island is a beautiful depiction of the life we dream of, capturing the moments we wish to experience beyond our daily routines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At present, the DEMO test session has been op